    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay so 1.7 units. but i actually took a small dose like 20 mins ago for a snack, so i might be a bit \"stacked\". if i take the full 1.7 now to make sure i hit that 100 for my presentation, will that be okay? or should i just round up to 2 units to be safe and make sure it definitely works? i really can't afford to be high during this meeting.",
